---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SEO from "../components/SEO.astro";
---

<BaseLayout currentPath="/about/">
  <SEO
    slot="head"
    title="About Us"
    description="China AI Tutorials helps global developers learn to use Chinese AI tools. Learn about our mission and team."
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-title">About China AI Tutorials</h1>

      <div class="prose">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Chinese AI tools are evolving at an unprecedented pace. Products like DeepSeek, Kimi (Moonshot AI),
          Qwen (Tongyi Qianwen), and Doubao have drawn significant global attention. Yet,
          <strong>high-quality English tutorials remain critically scarce</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Most Chinese-language tutorials are never translated into English, and the scattered
          discussions in English-speaking communities often stay at a surface level.
          China AI Tutorials was created to bridge this gap.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>In-depth tutorials</strong>: No armchair theory. Every tutorial includes runnable code examples, tested against the latest API versions.</li>
          <li><strong>Chinese-English bridge</strong>: We dive into official Chinese documentation and community knowledge, then present it in fluent, idiomatic English.</li>
          <li><strong>Independent reviews</strong>: No sponsored content. All model comparisons are based on real, measured data.</li>
          <li><strong>Continuously updated</strong>: Every tutorial is marked "Last updated: Month 202X." We refresh content promptly when APIs change.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
          The site founder is a developer familiar with the Chinese AI ecosystem. While using these tools,
          they noticed that most of the friction overseas developers encountered when integrating Chinese AI APIs
          stemmed from a lack of clear English documentation.
        </p>
        <p>
          And so, in June 2026, China AI Tutorials was born.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have tutorial suggestions, spot an error, or want to collaborate, feel free to visit the
          <a href="/contact/">contact page</a> or email us at <code>hello@china-ai-tutorials.com</code>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .section { padding: var(--space-2xl) 0; }
  .page-title { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl); }

  .prose h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .prose ul {
    margin-left: var(--space-lg);
  }
</style>
